title: Property-based conformance tests for shell safety (Coq vs OCaml)
---
Generate random shell strings (including metacharacters, quotes, spaces, unicode). Assert Clawq_core.is_shell_safe vs has_unsafe_shell_syntax_ocaml and Clawq_core.split_words vs split_command_words_ocaml agree on all inputs. Acceptance: make test includes shell safety conformance tests.